  "notes": "3rd great-grandmother. Born c. 1810 in Washington DC (from daughter's 1920 census). Married James Gordon on December 2, 1830 in Washington DC. Four children: Thomas H. (c. 1835), James H. (1837-1869), Elizabeth Ann (1840-1920), George M. (1848-1863). Son George died August 11, 1863 at age 15. Died April 26, 1867 in Washington DC. Buried in Washington, DC."
